theorem
fixes f :: "int \<Rightarrow> int"
assumes h0 : "\<forall> x. f x = (if x = 1 then 3 else if x = 2 then 1 else if x = 3 then 5 else if x = 4 then 4 else if x = 5 then 2 else undefined)"
and h1 : "bij f"
shows  "(inv f) ((inv f) ((inv f) 1)) = 3"
